msgstr "Sýna útflutningsglugga þegar útflutningur lýkur"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../preferences.rst:343
msgid ""
"The ComfyUI **Check** button updates an inline status icon: green checkmark "
"for success, red icon for failure. If OpenShot cannot reach this server, AI "
"context menu options are hidden. See :ref:`ai_ref` for setup details, "
"requirements, and workflow options."
msgstr ""
"ComfyUI **Athuga** hnappurinn uppfærir stöðutákn í línu: grænt hakmerki "
"fyrir árangur, rautt tákn fyrir bilun. Ef OpenShot nær ekki sambandi við "
"þennan þjón, eru valkostir í AI samhengisvalmynd falnir. Sjá :ref:`ai_ref` "
"fyrir uppsetningarupplýsingar, kröfur og vinnuflæðisvalkosti."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../preferences.rst:350
msgid "Reset (Default Values)"
msgstr "Endurstilla (sjálfgefin gildi)"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../preferences.rst:352
msgid ""
"To reset **all** preferences to their default values, please delete the "
"``openshot.settings`` file and re-launch OpenShot. The settings file can be "
"located at this path: ``~/.openshot_qt/openshot.settings`` or ``C:"
"\\Users\\USERNAME\\.openshot_qt\\openshot.settings``. When OpenShot is re-"
"launched, it will create the missing ``openshot.settings`` file with default "
"values."
msgstr ""
"Til að endurstilla **allar** stillingar í sjálfgefin gildi, vinsamlegast "
"eyðaðu ``openshot.settings`` skrá og ræstu OpenShot aftur. Stillingaskráin "
"er að finna á eftirfarandi slóð: ``~/.openshot_qt/openshot.settings`` eða "
"``C:\\Users\\NOTANDANAFN\\.openshot_qt\\openshot.settings``. Þegar OpenShot "
"er ræst aftur mun það búa til vantaða ``openshot.settings`` skrá með "
"sjálfgefnum gildum."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../preferences.rst:357
msgid ""
"Optionally, you can delete the entire ``.openshot_qt/`` folder and re-launch "
"OpenShot. However, please make a **backup** of any customized folders: "
"**emojis, presets, profiles, recovery, title_templates, transitions, or "
"yolo**. For example, your ``/recovery/`` sub-folder contains backup copies "
"of all your existing projects (``*.osp`` files)."
msgstr ""
"Auk þess getur þú eytt allri ``.openshot_qt/`` möppunni og ræst OpenShot "
"aftur. Vinsamlegast gerðu þó **afrit** af sérsniðnum möppum: **emojis, "
"presets, profiles, recovery, title_templates, transitions, eða yolo**. Til "
"dæmis inniheldur ``/recovery/`` undirmappa afrit af öllum núverandi "
"verkefnum þínum (``*.osp`` skrár)."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../preferences.rst:362
msgid ""
"Deleting the ``.openshot_qt/`` folder is the quickest method to restore "
"OpenShot preferences and settings to their Default values (i.e. also called "
"a `clean install`). When OpenShot is re-launched, it will create any missing "
"folders (i.e. ``.openshot_qt/``) and settings files. See our `step-by-step "
"guide <https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/wiki/Clean-Installation-of-"
"OpenShot>`_ for more information about **clean installs** of OpenShot."
msgstr ""
"Að eyða ``.openshot_qt/`` möppunni er hraðasta leiðin til að endurheimta "
"OpenShot stillingar og valkosti í sjálfgefna stöðu (einnig kallað `hrein "
"uppsetning`). Þegar OpenShot er ræst aftur mun það búa til allar vantar "
"möppur (t.d. ``.openshot_qt/``) og stillingarskrár. Sjáðu okkar `skref-fyrir-"
"skref leiðbeiningar <https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/wiki/Clean-"
"Installation-of-OpenShot>`_ fyrir frekari upplýsingar um **hreinar "
"uppsetningar** OpenShot."
